title: FF 010 (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description: They've handled media mockery, crippling self-doubt, kidnapping, and the greatest fiends the Negative Zone could throw at them -- but can the FF handle? THE SPOOKY KIDS?SHIVER! As they write the names of weird bands you've never heard of ALL OVER their desktops!QUAKE! As they use strange "slang" to hide their true conversations! What are they talking about? Could be? ANYTHING.RECOIL! At their monstrous cell phone data plan bills every month. Seriously you have NO IDEA how much these kids use their phones.The generation gap has come for the Future Foundation? BREAK OUT THE BLACK NAIL POLISH!
